
<div class="container" style="width: 200rem; margin-top: 75px;">

    <!-- Background ripple animation -->

  <div class='ripple-background'>
    <div class='circle xxlarge shade1'></div>
    <div class='circle xlarge shade2'></div>
    <div class='circle large shade3'></div>
    <div class='circle mediun shade4'></div>
    <div class='circle small shade5'></div>
  </div>

    <!-- Heading  -->

  <div>
    <br>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
        <h1 class="text-underline"><%= @album.album_name + " - " + @album.artist.artist_name %></h1>
      </div>
    <br>
  </div>

      <!-- Buttons -  -->

  <div class="flex-container justify-content-center">

    <div class="d-flex align-items center">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div><%= link_to "Search for #{@album.album_name} on discogs", "https://www.discogs.com/search/?type=all&title=#{@album.album_name}&artist=#{@album.artist.artist_name}&format=vinyl", class: "btn btn-primary mr-2", target: :blank %></div>
        <div><%= link_to 'Find a record store', sellers_path, class: "btn btn-primary mr-2" %></div>
        <div><%= link_to 'Go back to albums', :back, class: "btn btn-info" %></div>
      </div>
    </div>


  <div class="d-flex show-card row justify-content-center align-items-center m-3 pr-4">

        <!-- Featured album card -->

    <div class="card-vinyl m-3">
      <img src= <%= @album.artwork_url %> />
      <div class="card-vinyl-infos d-flex flex-column justify-content-center" style="height: 43%;">
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
          <li><h2><%= @album.album_name %></h2></li>
          <li><p><%= @album.record_label %></p></li>
          <li><p><%= @album.year %></p></li>
          <% @album.genre.each do |genre| %>
          <li><p><%= genre %></p></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>

        <% if @favourite == [] %>
          <%= link_to album_favourites_path(@album.id), method: :post do  %>
            <i class="fab fa-gratipay" id="favourite"></i>
            <% end %>
        <% else  %>
            <i class='fab fa-gratipay' id='favourite-red'></i>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

        <!-- Album tracks card -->

        <div class="justify-content-center">
          <div class="card-album-tracks">
            <h2 class="text-underline mb-4">Track listings</h2>
            <ol>
              <% @album.tracks.each_with_index do | track | %>
                <li><p><%= track %></p></li>
              <% end %>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


            <!-- Six degrees button -->
        </div>
      <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="six-degrees btn btn-basic mb-4 w-50" style="text-align: center;">Six Degrees Of Separation</div>


            <!-- Associated album cards -->

      <div class="row justify-content-center flag hidden">
        <div class="d-flex mb-4 card-six-degrees_container">
          <!-- <h2 class="text-underline mb-1 ">Linked Artists</h2> -->
          <% @associated_albums.each do | album | %>
            <div class="card-six-degrees">
              <img src= <%= album.artwork_url%> />
              <!-- <div class="h-100"> -->
                <div class="card-vinyl-infos h-100">
                  <h2 class="pt-2"><%= link_to "#{album.album_name}", album_path(album) %></h2>
                  <h3><%= album.artist.artist_name + " " +  album.year %></h3>
                  <div class="pt-4">
                    <h4>Why
                      <% if album.artist.artist_name == "Various"%>
                      <%= album.album_name %>
                      <% else %>
                      <%= album.artist.artist_name %>
                      <% end %>?</h4>
                    <p><%= album.associated_act ? album.associated_act.connection_description : nil %></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <!-- </div> -->
            </div>
          <% end %>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="album_trivia" class="card-trivia" align-items-center>
     <p id="album_name" class="hidden"> <%= @album.album_name%> <span style="display:hidden"><%= @album.artist.artist_name %></span></p>
    </div>

                <!-- Six Degrees blurb card -->

  <div class="card-six-info six-text col-10" style="margin:0 auto 50px auto;">
  <h2 style="color:#AC7FDD; padding:8px">What is Six Degrees of Separation?</h2>
        <p>Musicians like to mingle. They collaborate, change bands, cover each others songs and share producers.
        Six degrees of separation explores these links, by suggesting six albums all linked to each other by real world events. Starting from your chosen album,
        the next suggestion could be linked by a guitarist that played in both bands, a producer that worked on both albums, or acts that performed together onstage. The possibilities are endless.
        Opening a panorama of potential links; spanning different artists, genres or points in time; our six degrees are all routed in this exciting world of interlinking unities.
        </p>
  </div>


<%= javascript_pack_tag 'show.js' %>
</div>
